<p>All Competitive Sports participants are required to create an account on imleagues.com. This will help track your team's roster and stats. Once you have created an account it can be used in other sports on campus.</p>
<p>&nbsp;</p>
<h2>To create an IM Leagues account:</h2>
<p>1. Go to <a class="extLink" href="http://www.imleagues.com/" title="Im Leagues" target="_blank">imleagues.com</a> in your internet browser</p>
<p>2. Click the Signup link at the top right.</p>
<p><img alt="IM Leagues Signup Button" height="468" src="Images/Admin_Offices/Activities/Sports/Competitive/IM Leagues/IMLeagues.png" title="IMLeagues1" width="600" /></p>
<p>3. Then from the <em>"Select you school from here"</em> drop down menu type <em>"BYUI"</em>.</p>
<p><img alt="Dropdown Selection" height="266" src="Images/Admin_Offices/Activities/Sports/Competitive/IM Leagues/IMLeagues2.png" title="IMLeagues2" width="600" /></p>
<p>&nbsp;</p>
<p>4. The next page will then say you need a valid school email. Go ahead and put your BYUI email into the email field and fill in the rest of the required information. Fill in the Human Verification as it is displayed and then check that you agree to the terms and conditions.</p>
<p><img alt="Form" height="656" src="Images/Admin_Offices/Activities/Sports/Competitive/IM Leagues/IMLeagues3.png" title="IMleagues3" width="640" /></p>
<p>5. Now hit the Sign Up button.</p>
<p>6. Great! You are now registered for IM Leagues. <em>You will soon be added to the appropriate team by your Coordinator.</em></p>]]></BodyCopy><xPower Type="GroupStart" GroupStart="" Name="PageComponents" label="Page Components" readonly="false" hidden="false" required="false" Expanded=""><xPower Type="List" List="xpowercomponent_Optional" Name="OptionalColumnComponent" label="Optional Column Components" readonly="false" hidden="false" required="false" Component="" CompTypes="FacebookComponent;Image;ColumnTextComponent;Media;Quote" Expanded="false"><xPower Type="Component" Component="" Name="Optional" readonly="false" hidden="false" required="false" CompTypes="FacebookComponent;Image;ColumnTextComponent;Media;Quote" Expanded="false"/></xPower><xPower Type="Component" Component="" Name="QuickLinksColumn1" label="QuickLinks Column 1" readonly="false" hidden="false" required="false" CompTypes="QuickLinksComponent"/><xPower Type="Component" Component="" Name="QuickLinksColumn2" label="QuickLinks Column 2" readonly="false" hidden="false" required="false" CompTypes="QuickLinksComponent"/><xPower Type="Component" Component="" Name="QuickLinksColumn3" label="QuickLinks Column 3" readonly="false" hidden="false" required="false" CompTypes="QuickLinksComponent"/></xPower><xPower Type="Component" Component="x6793" Name="HighlightedLinks" label="Highlighted Links" readonly="false" hidden="false" required="false" CompTypes="HighlightedLinksComponent" Expanded="false"/><xPower Type="Navigation" StartPage="x5" MaxDepth="" MaxNodes="" GenerationOrder="down" Navigation="Ancestors" Query="" Name="AncestorNavigation" label="Ancestor Navigation" readonly="true" hidden="true" required="false" Expanded="false"/><xPower Type="Component" Component="x6784" Name="SiteControl" label="Site Control" readonly="true" hidden="false" required="false" CompTypes="SiteControl" Expanded="false"/></Content>
